name: "Haunting Eyes" Wolf Art Print
description:
This is an archival quality, open edition print of my original colored pencil drawing and is hand signed for you by myself, the artist, Carla Kurt. 

This print measures 10.5"x11.5"

Printed on heavy museum quality art paper with archival inks and looks just like the original.  The detail is outstanding.   

A wonderful addition to your art collection for your home or office,  or as the perfect gift for a friend!

The copyright watermark will not appear on the print you receive.

Please contact me for availability of the original artwork, and various sizes of prints available.
